headline: GoDaddy Inc. to Present at the UBS Global Technology Conference and Barclays Global Technology Conference
summary: GoDaddy Inc. (NYSE: GDDY) Chief Financial Officer Mark McCaffrey will present at the UBS Global Technology Conference in Scottsdale, Arizona on Wednesday, Dec. 4, 2024 at 10:15 a.m. ET / 7:15 a.m. PT as well as the Barclays Global Technology Conference in San Francisco, California on Thursday, Dec. 12, 2024 at 11:40 a.m. ET / 8:40 a.m. PT.
